\"text-align:center;\"|Best International Group\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Themselves\n|{{Nominated}}\n|rowspan=\"1\"|<ref>{{Cite web|title= Nominees announced for BreakTudo Awards 2018|url = https://celebmix.com/nominees-announced-for-breaktudo-awards-2018/|work=Celebmix |accessdate= August 29, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"1\"|[[:es: Tudo Information Awards|Tudo Information Awards]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Group of The Year\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Themselves\n|{{nominated}}\n|rowspan=\"1\"|<ref>{{Cite web|title= Tudo Information Awards 2018 abre suas vota\u00e7\u00f5es e Anitta, BTS, Selena Gomez, Luan Santana, Bia Arantes e Kaysar est\u00e3o entre os indicados|url = https://www.clickparana.com/noticia/20191/tudo-information-awards-2018-abre-suas-votacoes-e-anitta-bts-selena-gomez-luan-santana-bia-arantes-e-kaysar-estao-entre-os-indicados.html|work=Clik Paran\u00e1 |accessdate= August 29, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= BTS, Camila Cabello, BlackPink and Mamamoo are nominated at the Brazilian Tudo Information Awards 2018|url = https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/12/bts-camila-cabello-blackpink-and-mamamoo-are-nominated-at-the-brazilian-tudo-information-awards-2018|work=Allkpop|accessdate= August 29, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[2019 Billboard Latin Music Awards|Billboard Latin Music Awards]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |Latin Pop Artist of the Year, Duo or Group\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |Themselves\n|{{Won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Latin Pop Album of the Year\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''CNCO''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Latin Rhythm Artist of the Year, Duo or Group\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Themselves\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | The Pop Hub Awards\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Najlepsza Choreografia (Best Choreography)\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | \"Pretend\"\n|{{Pending}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Ulubiona Trasa Koncertowa (Favorite Concert Tour)\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCO World Tour\n|{{Pending}}\n|-\n| Ulubiona Gwiazda Latynoska (Favorite Latin Star)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''CNCO''\n|{{Pending}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Latin American Music Awards of 2019|Latin AMAs]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Favorite Duo or Group\t\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCO\n|{{won}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|<ref name=\"nominados\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.infobae.com/america/entretenimiento/2019/09/04/la-lista-completa-de-los-nominados-a-los-latin-american-music-awards/|title=La lista completa de los nominados a los Latin American Music Awards|first=4 De Septiembre|last=De 2019|website=Infobae}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Favorite Pop Artist\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCO\n|{{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[2019 MTV Video Music Awards]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Push Artist of the Year\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCO\n|{{nominated}}\n|rowspan='2'|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://us.hola.com/celebrities/2019082627357/cnco-hola-usa-interview-exclusive/|title=CNCO talks about their headlining tour, MTV VMAs surprises|date=August 26, 2019|website=HOLA USA}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | Best Group\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCO\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[BreakTudo Awards 2019|BreakTudo Awards]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | International Fandom \n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | CNCOwners\n|{{Pending}}\n|<ref name=\"nominees\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.midiorama.com/anitta-e-ariana-grande-lideram-lista-de-indicados-do-breaktudo-awards-2019-veja-os-destaques|title=Anitta e Ariana Grande lideram lista de indicados do BreakTudo Awards 2019. Veja os destaques! &#124; Midiorama|website=www.midiorama.com}}</ref> \n|-\n|}\n\n=== Others ===\n\n==== Latin American Music Awards ====\n2016\n*New Artist of the Year ('''Won''')\n*New Favorite Artist - Pop/Rock ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Duo or Group - Pop/Rock ('''Won''')\n2017\n*Favorite Duo or Group - Pop/Rock ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Pop/Rock Song - Reggaeton Lento ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Pop Album - Primera Cita ('''Won''')\n*Album of the Year - Primer Cita ('''Won''')\n2018\n*Favorite Duo or Group ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Pop Album - CNCO ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Pop Artist ('''Wo'''n)\n2019\n*Favorite Duo or Group ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Pop Artist ('''Won''')\n\n==== Premios Tu Mundo ====\n2017\n*Favorite Pop Artist \u2013 Themselves ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Party-Starter Song \u2013 \"Hey DJ\" ft. Yandel ('''Won''')\n*Favorite Fan Club \u2013 CNCOwners ('''Won''')\n\n==== Premio Lo Nuestro ====\n\n*Social Artist of the Year - Themselves (Nominated)<ref name=\"auto\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.etonline.com/2019-premio-lo-nuestro-complete-list-of-winners-119827|title=2019 Premio Lo Nuestro: Complete List of Winners|website=Entertainment Tonight}}</ref>\n*Pop/Rock Group or Duo of the Year - Themselves ('''Won''')<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n\n==== Billboard Music Awards ====\n\n*Top Latin Album \u2013 ''Primera Cita'' (Nominated)\n\n==== Teen Choice Awards ====\n2017\n*Choice Latin Artist \u2013 Themselves ('''Won''')\n*Choice Latin Song \u2013 \"Reggaeton Lento (Bailemos)\" (Nominated)\n*Choice International Artist \u2013 Themselves (Nominated)\n2018\n*Choice Latin Artist \u2013 Themselves ('''Won''')\n*Choice Latin Song \u2013 \"Hey DJ feat Yandel\" (Nominated)\n*Choice International Artist \u2013 Themselves (Nominated)\n*Choice Fandom \u2013 CNCOwners (Nominated)\n2019\n*Choice Latin Artist \u2013 Themselves ('''Won''')\n*Choice Latin Song \u2013 \"Pretend\" ('''Won''')\n*Choice International Artist \u2013 Themselves (Nominated)\n*Choice Fandom \u2013 CNCOwners (Nomi